msgid ""
"Istio self-signed certificates have historically had a 1 year default "
"lifetime. If you are using Istio self-signed certificates, you need to be"
" mindful about the expiration date of the root certificate. The "
"expiration of a root certificate may lead to an unexpected cluster-wide "
"outage."
