#: ../../source/docs/ops/configuration/security/root-transition/index.rst:14
msgid ""
"The steps below show you how to transition to a new root certificate. "
"After the transition, the new root certificate has a 10 year lifetime. "
"Note that the Envoy instances will be hot restarted to reload the new "
"root certificates, which may impact long-lived connections. For details "
"about the impact and how Envoy hot restart works, please refer to `here "
"<https://www.envoyproxy.io/docs/envoy/latest/intro/arch_overview/operations/hot_restart>`_"
" and `here <https://blog.envoyproxy.io/envoy-hot-restart-1d16b14555b5>`_."
